erto Rican [[boxing|boxer]]. He competed in the [[Boxing at the 1988 Summer Olympics \u2013 Lightweight|men's lightweight]] event at the [[1988 Summer Olympics]].<ref name=\"SportsRef\">{{cite Sports-Reference |url=https://www.sports-reference.com/olympics/athletes/ar/hector-arroyo-1.html |title=H\u00e9ctor Arroyo |accessdate=4 January 2019}}</ref>\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n* {{IOC profile|hector-a-arroyo|Hector A. Arroyo}}\n\n{{Authority control}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Arroyo, Hector}}\n[[Category:1966 births]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:Puerto Rican male boxers]]\n[[Category:Olympic boxers of Puerto Rico]]\n[[Category:Boxers at the 1988 Summer Olympics]]\n[[Category:People from Morovis, Puerto Rico]]\n\n\n{{PuertoRico-boxing-bio-stub}}\n", "name_user": "Jevansen", "label": "safe", "comment": "addedCategory:Pan American Games medalists in boxing", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/H%C3%A9ctor_Arroyo"}
{"title_page": "Wanderley Oliveira", "text_new": "{{short description|Brazilian boxer}}\n{{Use dmy dates|date=January 2019}}\n{{Infobox sportsperson\n| name           = Wanderley Oliveira\n| full_name      = \n| image          = \n| caption        = \n| nationality    = Brazilian\n| sport          = [[Boxing]]\n| birth_date     = {{birth date and age|1965|3|29|df=yes}}\n| birth_place    = [[S\u00e3o Paulo]], Brazil\n| death_date     = \n| death_place    = \n}}\n\n'''Wanderley Oliveira''' (born 29 March 1965) is a Brazilian [[boxing|boxer]]. He competed in the [[Boxing at the 1988 Summer Olympics \u2013 Welterweight|men's welterweight]] event at the [[1988 Summer Olympics]].<ref name=\"SportsRef\">{{cite Sports-Reference |url=https://www.sports-reference.com/olympics/athletes/ol/wanderley-oliveira-1.html |title=Wanderley Oliveira Olympic Results |accessdate=5 January 2019}}</ref>\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n\n{{Authority control}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Oliveira, Wanderley}}\n[[Category:1965 births]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:Brazilian male boxers]]\n[[Category:Olympic boxers of Brazil]]\n[[Category:Boxers at the 1988 Summer Olympics]]\n[[Category:Sportspeople from S\u00e3o Paulo]]\n[[Category:Pan American Games medalists in boxing]]\n\n\n{{Brazil-boxing-bio-stub}}\n", "text_old": "{{short description|Brazilian boxer}}\n{{Use dmy dates|date=January 2019}}\n{{Infobox sportsperson\n| name           = Wanderley Oliveira\n| full_name      = \n| image          = \n| caption        = \n| nationality    = Brazilian\n| sport          = [[Boxing]]\n| birth_date     = {{birth date and age|1965|3|29|df=yes}}\n| birth_place    = [[S\u00e3o Paulo]], Brazil\n| death_date     = \n| death_place    = \n}}\n\n'''Wanderley Oliveira''' (born 29 March 1965) is a Brazilian [[boxing|boxer]]. He competed in the [[Boxing at the 1988 Summer Olympics \u2013 Welterweight|men's welterweight]] event at the [[1988 Summer Olympics]].<ref name=\"SportsRef\">{{cite Sports-Reference |url=h